{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Five stories. Thousands of raw wounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>R/A\\W</strong> is a collection of anti-war visual novels developed over the past three years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>NO WAY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sasha drives home along the country roads, pacing from stop to stop, as she calls on Agnia, who is... not doing well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's going to be a small and personal story, as if out of our world, isn't it?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE BEAST</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story of two ordinary guys trapped in a war, facing a difficult choice: inevitable doom tomorrow or the shame of desertion today.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>NEW ANGEL SANCTUARY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Shenetz returns to his once abandoned homeland and meets a girl who has defeated Death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What happened to her and the place over the years?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <strong>FAREWELL TO DERE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Fog, which sows anger and hatred, covers the City, but no one but the protagonist notices it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To stop the Fog, he sacrifices everything.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>AND THE SILENCE FALLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The day has come when we are forbidden to tell the truth.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All that's left is Music, the most complex and the most understandable language.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737723534","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445290/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737723534","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445290/20ae3a41045c1b1f85497f1ee97630626066adaf/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=